icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Electric Vehicle Charging Stations</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472096\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h4>Electric vehicle (EV) charging stations are located in Grand Canyon Village (South Rim)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><b>No EV charging is available at Desert View or on the North Rim.</b></li>\n<li><em>All EV chargers around the Village are Level II, open to the public, and free of charge.</em></li>\n<li><em>While most of the EV chargers in the park offer a J1772 type plug, three Tesla chargers are available at Yavapai Lodge East.</em></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472550\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472550\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472167\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472167\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"a map of Grand Canyon Village showing the 2 locations where electric vehicle charging stations are located, 1) at Market Plaza and Yavapai Lodge East, and 2) a Maswik Lodge on the west end of the Village Historic District.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/village_map_EV_copy-3-16-23-copy.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"village_map_EV_copy-3-16-23 copy\"/>\n<figcaption>As seen in this overview map of the Grand Canyon Village on the South Rim, electric vehicle (EV) charging stations are located in two areas. 1) In the center of the village at Market Plaza and at Yavapai Lodge East, and 2) At Maswik Lodge on the west side of the Village Historic District. Scroll down the page for precise locations and more detailed maps. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472265\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472265\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Market Plaza and Yavapai Lodge East </h2>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472521\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472521\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"3 photos: 1 - red car at an EV charging station on large parking lot, 2- map showing the locations of EV charging stations at Market Plaza and Yavapai Lodge, 3 - EV charger along parking lot of 2 story green and brown building.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/market-plaza-yavapai-east-collage-copy-copy.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Grand Canyon National Park offers electric vehicle (EV) charging stations in and around Grand Canyon Village.\"/>\n<figcaption>Left Photo: (2) J1772 chargers on the north end of Parking Lot B, next to the shuttle bus stop at Yavapai Lodge are out of service until further notice. Right Photo: Two of six EV chargers in front of Yavapai Lodge East, Building One. At this location there are (3) J1772 chargers, and (3) Tesla chargers. (These are the only Tesla chargers in the park.) All EV chargers around the village are open to the public, and free of charge. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS photos</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472536\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472536\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-3411CDA2-9420-0A46-B0085162AA9EC5F0\">\n<h2>While Your Vehicle is Charging by Yavapai Lodge</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-3411CDA2-9420-0A46-B0085162AA9EC5F0\">Narrow By Location:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-3411CDA2-9420-0A46-B0085162AA9EC5F0\">Narrow By Office:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-count-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-count-form\"><p><label for=\"result-count-select-searchListing-3411CDA2-9420-0A46-B0085162AA9EC5F0\">Show</label><select id=\"result-count-select-searchListing-3411CDA2-9420-0A46-B0085162AA9EC5F0\" name=\"result-maxRows\">\n<option value=\"10\">10</option>\n<option value=\"40\">40</option>\n</select></p></form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><!--display-list-view-->\n<div class=\"FilterTags\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\n<div class=\"ListingResults-loading\">\nLoading results...\n</div>\n<ul class=\"resultsUL\"></ul>\n</div><!--results-->\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n<div class=\"resultsPaginationArea\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472286\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472286\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Maswik Lodge — North and South</h2>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472545\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472545\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"a series of 3 photos that show electric vehicle charging stations in relation to lodge buildings, with a location map with a photo on either side of the map.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Maswik-EV-collage-short.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Maswik Lodge EV Charging Stations\"/>\n<figcaption>Maswik Lodge has a total of seven EV charging stations. Left Photo: Maswik Lodge North has two J1772 chargers in front of the single story building named Cliffrose. Right Photo: Maswik Lodge South had four J1772 chargers on the west side of the two story lodge buildings. A single Handicap charging station is located on the east side of the lodge buildings, and is indicated by the ISA symbol on the map.  All EV chargers around the village are open to the public, and free of charge. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS photos.</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7472548\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7472548\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-3411F755-9D13-AAAB-A856EF783FC6BAA3\">\n<h2>While Your Vehicle Is Charging at Maswik Lodge</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-3411F755-9D13-AAAB-A856EF783FC6BAA3\">Narrow By Location:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-3411F755-9D13-AAAB-A856EF783FC6BAA3\">Narrow By Office:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-count-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-count-form\"><p><label for=\"result-count-select-searchListing-3411F755-9D13-AAAB-A856EF783FC6BAA3\">Show</label><select id=\"result-count-select-searchListing-3411F755-9D13-AAAB-A856EF783FC6BAA3\" name=\"result-maxRows\">\n<option value=\"10\">10</option>\n<option value=\"40\">40</option>\n</select></p></form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><!--display-list-view-->\n<div class=\"FilterTags\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\n<div class=\"ListingResults-loading\">\nLoading results...\n</div>\n<ul class=\"resultsUL\"></ul>\n</div><!--results-->\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n<div class=\"resultsPaginationArea\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: November 29, 2025</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--go